<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">questions, answered</span>
      <h2>Before you reach out, here's what people usually want to know.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do I need to know AI to work with you? <span class="plus">+</span></summary>
        <p>Not at all. Most of my clients have never written a prompt before we start. I build the system and teach you how to use it &mdash; you don't need any prior experience.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How long does Brand MAGIC take? <span class="plus">+</span></summary>
        <p>Every business is different, but most clients move through the full process &mdash; Discover, Define, Build, Teach, and Shine &mdash; over a few focused weeks rather than months.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you write my content for me? <span class="plus">+</span></summary>
        <p>I build the system and teach the AI to sound like you, but the goal is for you to create content confidently on your own afterward &mdash; not to hand your voice over to someone else.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I use ChatGPT instead of Claude? <span class="plus">+</span></summary>
        <p>Yes. The Brand MAGIC Guide and AI Knowledge Base are built to work with either Claude or ChatGPT, so you can use whichever tool you're most comfortable with.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do I need to switch email providers, website platforms, or other tools I'm already using? <span class="plus">+</span></summary>
        <p>Nope. We build your marketing system using the tools you're already using &mdash; your current email provider, website platform, or whatever else is already part of your day-to-day. If I see a tool that might genuinely serve you better, I'll mention it, but that's always a suggestion, never a requirement. What you keep, what you switch, and what you try is entirely up to you.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What happens after the session? <span class="plus">+</span></summary>
        <p>You'll walk away with your Brand MAGIC Guide, Brand Voice Guide, custom AI workspace, prompt library, and a 30-day content strategy &mdash; plus a training session so you know exactly how to use it all.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is this only for women-owned businesses? <span class="plus">+</span></summary>
        <p>I built Social Magic specifically with women-owned service businesses in mind, and that's who I love working with most. If that's not you but you connect with the philosophy here, feel free to reach out and we can talk it through.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

